    "name": "Few Seconds - Many Deaths!",
    "steam_appid": 3259720,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259720/extras/86766628678c55ea53f499deb5a756cc.avif?t=1759136888\" width=890 height=234 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are <strong>Mercenaries</strong>. Your mission is to hunt down the most <strong>Powerful Creatures</strong>. Each of them has <strong>Unique Abilities</strong>, some of which can completely turn the <strong>Gameplay</strong> upside down!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They can <strong>interact with the Arena</strong>, <strong>possess Players</strong>, <strong>freeze Mouse Sensitivity</strong>, and much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259720/extras/cb119fde77634d3ec6abef42d02d713d.avif?t=1759136888\" width=890 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hit your Allies</strong>, <strong>Heal your Enemies</strong>! <strong>Steal Treasures</strong> from other players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is built around a <strong>Cooperative Experience</strong>. You can mess with your teammates in all sorts of ways or stick together as a <strong>United Team</strong> to overcome challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are 4 main classes in the game – <strong>Attacker</strong>, <strong>Defender</strong>, <strong>Healer</strong>, and <strong>Strategist</strong>. Deal <strong>Massive Damage</strong>, <strong>Remove Negative Effects</strong>, or use your abilities to <strong>Reposition Players in Battle</strong>. The choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And remember – <strong>Mistakes are Inevitable</strong>. Because...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259720/extras/1da3988ea1abcd47882d3e5ea160b323.avif?t=1759136888\" width=890 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time per Turn is Limited</strong>! <strong>VERY LIMITED</strong>! And in that time, you must <strong>Discuss Strategy</strong> with everyone and make a <strong>Brilliant Move</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But most likely… someone will <strong>Knock the Boss</strong> into the poor <strong>Healer</strong>. Which will cause the <strong>Attacker to Miss</strong>. The <strong>Healer</strong> will try to save the team, but then gets <strong>Teleported Away by the Strategist</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You do <strong>NOT see</strong> what your teammates are planning to do. That’s why it’s so important to <strong>Talk it Over</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Otherwise, someone may <strong>Die</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3259720/extras/7910dd6ec3110c6fa7a6b3df87867cc6.avif?t=1759136888\" width=890 height=232 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Random Events</strong>, <strong>Mysterious Artifacts</strong>, and numerous <strong>Bosses with Different Modifiers</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you and your friends overcome all challenges and become <strong>Legendary Mercenaries</strong>?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
